          <p class="col-md-4 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 intro-body">With a storyline based on the classic crossover series and a huge cast of heroes and villains at our disposal, we came up with several ways to excite hardcore and casual fans from the trailer’s first viewing at New York Comic Con until the game’s release date.
          <br>
          <br>
