            <p>An episodic prologue setting up the game's story arc. We worked with teams at Kabam! and Marvel to keep fans excited during the couple months between New York Comic Con and the game’s release. It introduces characters that might not be familiar to all fans and gives more context to the game’s main plot, all in familiar comic panels with some additional interactive elements.</p>
